# Welcome to rm3

If you can see this page, this means that [rm3](https://github.com/rm3web/rm3) is probably working correctly.  Welcome!

## Where to go from here?

Well, you probably want to be able to log in, don't you?  Click on the `Login` button in the right hand of the page to log in with whatever login credentials you created at startup (the instructions generally tell you to create an account called `wirehead` with a password of `password`.

You can create a new page by clicking on the `Create` drop down, or edit this page with the `Edit` button.
